data.description: This spacious, waterfront home is ready for a new family. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and two flex spaces, this home has a lot to offer within the 2,356 square feet. Outside you'll appreciate massive curb appeal, and a huge, fully fenced backyard with Great Lake views! The home is laid out with families and entertaining in mind, with all private bedrooms and baths upstairs. Private bath features a great jacuzzi soaking tub. The one half bath is downstairs to serve the open living and dining space. Plenty of storage in this home's two car garage and spacious closets. This home is walking distance to New Berlin Elementary, with an easy commute to the beaches, Mayport, and International Airport. Shopping is close by at River City Marketplace. Roof is only 3 years old.
